Type of Feat: Item Creation
Prerequisite: Spellcaster Level 9th+.
Specifics: You can create a rod of any spell of 6th level or less that you know. To create a rod, cast an appropriate spell on a bone rod in your inventory. Creating a rod costs gold pieces based on the relative power of the spell. Rods containing first level spells can cost a few thousand gold pieces while those made with higher level spells can cost tens of thousands. Warlock invocations cannot be used in the creation of rods. Newly crafted rods have 50 charges.
Use: Cast a spell on a bone rod in your inventory.